WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.570
Hey, good morning, everybody. I have some

00:00:02.580 --> 00:00:04.730
things I want to share with you about

00:00:04.740 --> 00:00:06.590
what the Lord has shown me about the

00:00:06.600 --> 00:00:11.810
work and its escalation.

00:00:11.820 --> 00:00:15.230
Here we go. I was praying, and then

00:00:15.240 --> 00:00:18.109
the Lord showed me the massive storm

00:00:18.119 --> 00:00:22.010
again. I keep telling you all, I see

00:00:22.020 --> 00:00:24.830
the storm on the East Coast, and

00:00:24.840 --> 00:00:26.990
it was getting closer and closer.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:28.609
But this time when I was

00:00:28.619 --> 00:00:31.490
praying, the Lord showed me our

00:00:31.500 --> 00:00:34.490
American soldiers all in a

00:00:34.490 --> 00:00:34.500
single-file

00:00:34.500 --> 00:00:37.130
line,

00:00:37.140 --> 00:00:39.530
and they were headed toward the

00:00:39.540 --> 00:00:41.930
European area.

00:00:41.940 --> 00:00:43.910
The Lord told me there

00:00:43.910 --> 00:00:43.920
is

00:00:43.920 --> 00:00:46.430
going to be a massive draft, and they

00:00:46.430 --> 00:00:46.440
are

00:00:46.440 --> 00:00:48.950
going to draft all these people into the

00:00:48.960 --> 00:00:53.510
war.

00:00:53.510 --> 00:00:53.520
Suddenly,

00:00:53.520 --> 00:00:54.650
the

00:00:54.650 --> 00:00:54.660
devil

00:00:54.660 --> 00:00:57.350
takes me to Europe. I

00:00:57.350 --> 00:00:57.360
do not

00:00:57.360 --> 00:01:00.770
know what this devil was or

00:01:00.780 --> 00:01:03.470
what it represented necessarily, other

00:01:03.480 --> 00:01:06.530
than it was some

00:01:06.540 --> 00:01:09.410
kind of demonic spirit of war.

00:01:09.420 --> 00:01:11.570
He was in a pit,

00:01:11.580 --> 00:01:14.390
and in the pit, he had these massive

00:01:14.400 --> 00:01:16.850
chains on his arms, and he was

00:01:16.860 --> 00:01:19.609
chained down.

00:01:19.609 --> 00:01:19.619
Suddenly,

00:01:19.619 --> 00:01:23.990
an angelic being—it was a

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:25.550
good one, an

00:01:25.550 --> 00:01:25.560
angel—came

00:01:25.560 --> 00:01:28.490
and took those chains

00:01:28.500 --> 00:01:31.370
off of that

00:01:31.380 --> 00:01:33.770
devil.

00:01:33.780 --> 00:01:37.130
He shot up out of the ground and

00:01:37.140 --> 00:01:40.490
was spinning like a top. He

00:01:40.500 --> 00:01:42.890
had these massive Viking

00:01:42.900 --> 00:01:46.249
horns on his head, and he had

00:01:46.259 --> 00:01:50.050
this fur with a

00:01:50.060 --> 00:01:53.810
leather sash across his chest.

00:01:53.820 --> 00:01:56.270
He had this fur, like a

00:01:56.270 --> 00:01:56.280
white-looking

00:01:56.280 --> 00:01:58.130
fur,

00:01:58.130 --> 00:01:58.140
polar-bear-looking

00:01:58.140 --> 00:02:02.990
outfit, like a Viking outfit.

00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:05.929
He started spinning and

00:02:05.939 --> 00:02:10.070
went inside of Vladimir Putin, and

00:02:10.080 --> 00:02:13.970
his whole countenance changed. He

00:02:13.980 --> 00:02:17.630
became energized, almost like he

00:02:17.630 --> 00:02:17.640
had

00:02:17.640 --> 00:02:20.089
lost his mind.

00:02:20.099 --> 00:02:22.430
It was weird, the way

00:02:22.440 --> 00:02:24.530
the Lord showed me. Suddenly, I

00:02:24.540 --> 00:02:28.010
want to show you—I have a picture here—so I could show you where I see

00:02:28.020 --> 00:02:31.670
the

00:02:31.680 --> 00:02:35.390
rocket. Do

00:02:35.400 --> 00:02:37.550
you have it on there, son?

00:02:37.560 --> 00:02:40.910
I saw a rocket come out of Russia and

00:02:40.920 --> 00:02:42.410
hit right here,

00:02:42.420 --> 00:02:45.470
right up in this area of Poland. It

00:02:45.480 --> 00:02:48.229
was a massive hit right next to here,

00:02:48.239 --> 00:02:50.150
in the

00:02:50.160 --> 00:02:51.410
corner.

00:02:51.420 --> 00:02:53.330
He was

00:02:53.340 --> 00:02:56.930
attacking this area with

00:02:56.940 --> 00:03:00.710
a massive bomb, but it was not

00:03:00.720 --> 00:03:03.410
anything that has ever been used

00:03:03.420 --> 00:03:05.750
before. Whenever I saw it happen,

00:03:05.760 --> 00:03:08.930
I said, "Oh no, he's using nuclear

00:03:08.930 --> 00:03:08.940
weapons."And

00:03:08.940 --> 00:03:12.170
the Lord said, "No, he is not. This is

00:03:12.180 --> 00:03:14.330
something that has never been used

00:03:14.340 --> 00:03:17.449
before on the Earth."He said, "This is a

00:03:17.459 --> 00:03:20.270
new technology."It was like it

00:03:20.280 --> 00:03:23.570
vaporized everybody, but it

00:03:23.580 --> 00:03:25.670
wasn't of the radiation and all this

00:03:25.680 --> 00:03:28.250
stuff.

00:03:28.260 --> 00:03:29.390
I've never seen anything like that

00:03:29.400 --> 00:03:31.729
before. The Lord said that

00:03:31.739 --> 00:03:33.290
nobody else had either; it's never been

00:03:33.300 --> 00:03:36.890
used before. Then

00:03:36.900 --> 00:03:39.890
I saw

00:03:44.900 --> 00:03:47.990
Turkey.

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:51.350
From here over, there were these massive,

00:03:55.080 --> 00:03:59.509
humongous drums beating. I said,

00:03:59.509 --> 00:03:59.519
"Lord, what are

00:03:59.519 --> 00:04:01.789
they

00:04:01.799 --> 00:04:04.070
doing?"and

00:04:04.080 --> 00:04:05.990
He said, "They're going to

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:09.050
join in and make ties.

00:04:09.060 --> 00:04:10.850
They're going to make some kind of

00:04:10.860 --> 00:04:12.649
financial agreements. There are going to be

00:04:12.659 --> 00:04:15.110
things that happen with them going in with

00:04:15.120 --> 00:04:17.449
Russia, and they're going to join in on

00:04:17.459 --> 00:04:19.849
the fight to help fund them and do

00:04:19.859 --> 00:04:21.590
things, and it's going to

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:24.710
escalate even

00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:25.430
further."This

00:04:25.440 --> 00:04:28.189
thing got out of control.

00:04:28.199 --> 00:04:32.689
Then I was shown

00:04:32.699 --> 00:04:34.969
Israel.

00:04:34.969 --> 00:04:34.979
Iran

00:04:34.979 --> 00:04:38.150
and these

00:04:38.160 --> 00:04:40.610
other countries were all coming against

00:04:40.620 --> 00:04:41.870
Israel.

00:04:41.880 --> 00:04:44.210
But the United States

00:04:44.220 --> 00:04:46.249
turned

00:04:46.249 --> 00:04:46.259
our

00:04:46.259 --> 00:04:49.790
back. We turned our back, doing nothing.

00:04:49.800 --> 00:04:52.129
The Lord said, "This is what's going to

00:04:52.139 --> 00:04:55.670
happen during the Ezekiel 38 and

00:04:55.680 --> 00:04:57.430
39

00:04:57.430 --> 00:04:57.440
War."People

00:04:57.440 --> 00:04:59.689
have always wondered, "Where's the

00:04:59.699 --> 00:05:02.150
United States in

00:05:02.150 --> 00:05:02.160
this?"We

00:05:02.160 --> 00:05:04.430
don't do anything. We don't help them.

00:05:04.440 --> 00:05:06.409
We just kind

00:05:06.419 --> 00:05:07.969
of watch, idly stand by and just watch.

00:05:07.979 --> 00:05:09.530
That's what I saw.

00:05:09.540 --> 00:05:11.990
Then I saw

00:05:11.990 --> 00:05:12.000
that

00:05:12.000 --> 00:05:16.670
because we betrayed Israel,

00:05:16.680 --> 00:05:20.810
we opened an attack for China to come in

00:05:20.820 --> 00:05:24.050
and get us. I saw China getting us.

00:05:26.940 --> 00:05:33.170
The surprise attack

00:05:33.180 --> 00:05:36.469
came as a dragon, and it looked like a

00:05:36.479 --> 00:05:39.170
red streaking dragon.

00:05:39.180 --> 00:05:41.810
Then the Lord showed me and He

00:05:41.820 --> 00:05:44.390
said, "Watch Hawaii."I could see Hawaii

00:05:44.400 --> 00:05:47.390
and all these F-16-looking fighter

00:05:47.400 --> 00:05:49.969
planes coming in, and they were just

00:05:49.979 --> 00:05:52.249
shooting missiles and going nuts on

00:05:52.259 --> 00:05:54.529
Honolulu and all these areas. I could

00:05:54.539 --> 00:05:57.050
see the main city there, Honolulu,

00:05:57.060 --> 00:05:59.390
Hawaii, and it was

00:05:59.400 --> 00:06:01.490
being annihilated

00:06:01.500 --> 00:06:04.430
with missiles and everything.

00:06:04.440 --> 00:06:06.529
Buildings were on fire and things were

00:06:06.539 --> 00:06:09.110
being shot down. It was a very

00:06:09.120 --> 00:06:11.629
sad situation because you could

00:06:11.639 --> 00:06:13.730
hear the sirens. I could hear

00:06:13.740 --> 00:06:15.590
some kind of air-raid sirens going off.

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:17.570
People were running and screaming

00:06:17.580 --> 00:06:19.129
and trying to get away, but there

00:06:19.129 --> 00:06:19.139
was

00:06:19.139 --> 00:06:21.590
nowhere to escape because it's an island.

00:06:21.600 --> 00:06:24.529
People were

00:06:24.539 --> 00:06:26.150
fighting back and everything, but it was

00:06:26.160 --> 00:06:30.409
a serious issue. The

00:06:30.409 --> 00:06:30.419
virus,

00:06:30.419 --> 00:06:31.909
this is some of the things the Lord

00:06:31.919 --> 00:06:33.469
shows me. I don't always want to

00:06:33.479 --> 00:06:36.070
come on and be like

00:06:36.070 --> 00:06:36.080
a

00:06:36.080 --> 00:06:38.629
fearmonger or whatever you all would

00:06:38.639 --> 00:06:40.969
say, that he always has negative news. I'm

00:06:40.979 --> 00:06:44.210
just a watchman. I see and I pray, and

00:06:44.220 --> 00:06:46.790
the Lord shows me things to pray about

00:06:46.800 --> 00:06:49.610
and things that could come. Some

00:06:49.620 --> 00:06:51.529
things we can avert; some things we

00:06:51.539 --> 00:06:52.550
can't.

00:06:52.560 --> 00:06:54.529
When

00:06:54.539 --> 00:06:56.450
he told me about the virus

00:06:56.460 --> 00:07:00.170
coming, he showed me a massive wave.

00:07:00.180 --> 00:07:03.409
The wave came in and crashed the

00:07:03.419 --> 00:07:05.450
shore, and he told me this was the

00:07:05.460 --> 00:07:09.050
virus. Behind the virus

00:07:09.060 --> 00:07:11.950
was another massive,

00:07:11.960 --> 00:07:13.969
humongous wave.

00:07:13.979 --> 00:07:17.090
It was so big that it was

00:07:17.100 --> 00:07:20.270
frightening to look at.

00:07:20.280 --> 00:07:23.089
The Lord said as soon as

00:07:23.099 --> 00:07:26.390
this virus pulls back and starts to

00:07:26.400 --> 00:07:29.990
recede, another massive wave of a wake-up

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:32.749
call will hit the earth. It's not about

00:07:32.759 --> 00:07:35.150
America; this is the

00:07:35.160 --> 00:07:38.510
world. He

00:07:38.520 --> 00:07:39.830
said there will be another wake-up call,

00:07:42.419 --> 00:07:44.510
another wave of whatever this is.

00:07:44.520 --> 00:07:49.450
But this time he showed me a number:

00:07:49.460 --> 00:07:53.570
350 million people would perish during

00:07:53.580 --> 00:07:57.890
whatever happens.

00:07:57.900 --> 00:07:59.450
I thought it would be another

00:07:59.460 --> 00:08:02.510
virus, like some kind of more serious

00:08:02.520 --> 00:08:05.629
thing, but I

00:08:05.639 --> 00:08:07.370
don't believe it is that. I believe it's

00:08:07.380 --> 00:08:09.050
something else. I don't know, and I don't want

00:08:09.060 --> 00:08:11.629
to assume. I just see and I don't

00:08:11.639 --> 00:08:13.550
want to add anything to it. I tell you

00:08:13.560 --> 00:08:15.890
exactly what I saw instead of

00:08:15.890 --> 00:08:15.900
saying,

00:08:15.900 --> 00:08:17.930
'I assume this,'because you

00:08:17.940 --> 00:08:20.089
get in a lot of trouble doing that.

00:08:20.089 --> 00:08:20.099
I

00:08:20.099 --> 00:08:22.249
just want to say exactly what I saw

00:08:22.259 --> 00:08:24.170
to you and tell you what the Lord

00:08:24.180 --> 00:08:25.969
showed me. I

00:08:25.969 --> 00:08:25.979
saw

00:08:25.979 --> 00:08:28.670
350 million people.

00:08:28.680 --> 00:08:30.890
Then the Lord showed me a

00:08:30.890 --> 00:08:30.900
vision.

00:08:30.900 --> 00:08:33.469
It

00:08:33.469 --> 00:08:33.479
was

00:08:33.479 --> 00:08:36.529
like

00:08:36.539 --> 00:08:38.029
a plane, and he said,

00:08:38.039 --> 00:08:41.449
'Like we plant, we sow, we

00:08:41.449 --> 00:08:41.459
reap.'He

00:08:41.459 --> 00:08:43.670
showed me people who are living

00:08:43.680 --> 00:08:46.070
Christians

00:08:46.070 --> 00:08:46.080
or

00:08:46.080 --> 00:08:48.949
pastors; if they're in hidden

00:08:48.959 --> 00:08:51.710
sin, they would be on the stage

00:08:51.720 --> 00:08:53.389
and just fall over dead like

00:08:53.389 --> 00:08:53.399
Ananias

00:08:53.399 --> 00:08:55.970
and Sapphira. It was going to be

00:08:55.980 --> 00:08:59.509
such a seed time acceleration of seed

00:08:59.519 --> 00:09:02.630
time and harvest of opening doors that

00:09:02.640 --> 00:09:04.610
the enemy comes in

00:09:04.620 --> 00:09:06.590
and just takes them out

00:09:06.600 --> 00:09:08.630
because of the open door they've

00:09:08.640 --> 00:09:11.389
caused. It was like

00:09:11.399 --> 00:09:13.310
an acceleration, a seedtime

00:09:13.310 --> 00:09:13.320
and

00:09:13.320 --> 00:09:16.430
harvest. It was very sad because

00:09:16.440 --> 00:09:18.050
there were people living in

00:09:18.050 --> 00:09:18.060
sin,

00:09:18.060 --> 00:09:19.910
pastors behind the pulpits and

00:09:19.920 --> 00:09:22.550
doing things. Christians living in an

00:09:22.560 --> 00:09:25.550
ungodly state were just dying.

00:09:25.560 --> 00:09:29.810
It wasn't just them;

00:09:29.820 --> 00:09:31.910
it was the world too. It was the people

00:09:31.920 --> 00:09:34.490
that weren't born again too.

00:09:35.880 --> 00:09:38.210
I'm trying to remember everything

00:09:39.660 --> 00:09:42.170
about that.

00:09:42.180 --> 00:09:44.690
Do you remember anything I'm leaving

00:09:44.700 --> 00:09:46.730
out? Because I talked about the people

00:09:46.740 --> 00:09:49.790
going home. It was very serious about all

00:09:49.800 --> 00:09:51.590
the people the Lord showed me going

00:09:51.600 --> 00:09:54.949
home. Thank you, Holy

00:09:54.959 --> 00:09:55.790
Ghost.

00:09:55.800 --> 00:09:58.670
He talked to me about an outpouring of

00:09:58.680 --> 00:10:03.590
finances. He showed me a small group

00:10:03.600 --> 00:10:06.590
of people. If you're praying,

00:10:06.600 --> 00:10:08.810
listening, keeping a

00:10:08.820 --> 00:10:10.910
fast life, and

00:10:10.920 --> 00:10:12.590
keeping your ear

00:10:12.590 --> 00:10:12.600
toward

00:10:12.600 --> 00:10:15.290
him,

00:10:15.300 --> 00:10:17.570
listening for his every word,

00:10:17.580 --> 00:10:21.230
he said there was

00:10:21.240 --> 00:10:24.850
going to be a supernatural

00:10:24.860 --> 00:10:28.670
outpouring of finances on a select few

00:10:28.680 --> 00:10:31.210
people,

00:10:31.220 --> 00:10:34.430
like inventions. I know how some of it

00:10:34.440 --> 00:10:36.530
happens, but I don't feel like I can talk

00:10:36.540 --> 00:10:39.050
about it.

00:10:39.060 --> 00:10:41.269
He showed me that the finances would come

00:10:41.279 --> 00:10:43.430
because he told

00:10:43.440 --> 00:10:44.810
me about the crash. There is going to be a

00:10:44.820 --> 00:10:46.370
massive crash;

00:10:46.380 --> 00:10:48.350
it's part of whenever

00:10:48.360 --> 00:10:50.389
they bring in the digital dollar and all

00:10:50.399 --> 00:10:52.670
the things. And I said, "Lord, how are these massive ministries going

00:10:52.670 --> 00:10:52.680
to happen and support

00:10:52.680 --> 00:10:55.610
these

00:10:55.620 --> 00:10:58.250
people?"This

00:10:58.260 --> 00:11:00.110
is something else he

00:11:00.120 --> 00:11:01.850
showed me because I was thinking

00:11:01.850 --> 00:11:01.860
about

00:11:01.860 --> 00:11:02.990
how people are going to get

00:11:03.000 --> 00:11:05.030
finances just to keep preaching the

00:11:05.040 --> 00:11:08.090
gospel. This is a big

00:11:08.100 --> 00:11:10.030
deal if another

00:11:10.040 --> 00:11:11.930
depression

00:11:11.940 --> 00:11:14.810
happens, similar to what occurred

00:11:14.810 --> 00:11:14.820
in the

00:11:14.820 --> 00:11:18.350
1920s and 1930s when the depression

00:11:18.350 --> 00:11:18.360
happened.

00:11:18.360 --> 00:11:21.590
He told me about

00:11:21.590 --> 00:11:21.600
supernatural provision.

00:11:21.600 --> 00:11:24.190
He said there will be an elite group

00:11:24.200 --> 00:11:28.490
that will walk in a

00:11:28.500 --> 00:11:31.430
financial outpouring that will bring in

00:11:31.440 --> 00:11:34.550
the money and help people.

00:11:34.560 --> 00:11:36.110
They'll be like a man with the pitcher

00:11:36.110 --> 00:11:36.120
in

00:11:36.120 --> 00:11:38.150
hand, helping out

00:11:38.160 --> 00:11:41.150
these ministries.

00:11:41.160 --> 00:11:44.509
I saw people because there was

00:11:44.519 --> 00:11:46.610
such a lack of food and supplies

00:11:46.610 --> 00:11:46.620
at

00:11:46.620 --> 00:11:48.530
the grocery stores.

00:11:49.980 --> 00:11:52.850
They will be at their dinner tables

00:11:52.860 --> 00:11:56.810
with empty pots, and the Lord showed me

00:11:56.820 --> 00:11:59.930
they will pray as a family around those

00:11:59.940 --> 00:12:01.730
empty pots. The Lord said, "I'm going

00:12:01.740 --> 00:12:05.870
to put food into those empty

00:12:05.870 --> 00:12:05.880
pots."I

00:12:05.880 --> 00:12:08.090
saw all kinds of

00:12:08.100 --> 00:12:10.389
soups and things that he provided

00:12:10.399 --> 00:12:12.590
supernaturally, just coming into those

00:12:12.600 --> 00:12:14.930
pots and filling them up every time they

00:12:14.940 --> 00:12:17.329
gathered around and gave him praise

00:12:17.339 --> 00:12:20.030
at the dinner table.

00:12:20.040 --> 00:12:22.970
Because the Bible says, "I never seen the

00:12:22.980 --> 00:12:25.610
righteous forsaken or their seed begging

00:12:25.620 --> 00:12:27.410
bread."And

00:12:27.420 --> 00:12:30.230
I believe with all my heart that

00:12:30.240 --> 00:12:32.030
even during all the drama that's going

00:12:32.040 --> 00:12:34.850
to take place before we go

00:12:34.850 --> 00:12:34.860
home—the

00:12:34.860 --> 00:12:37.190
birthing pains that are manifested on

00:12:37.200 --> 00:12:41.210
this Earth—we will see a supernatural

00:12:41.220 --> 00:12:43.910
provision just like the children of

00:12:43.920 --> 00:12:46.550
Israel had in the desert when he

00:12:46.560 --> 00:12:48.470
came in with the manna

00:12:48.480 --> 00:12:50.870
and took care of them with the quail. He

00:12:50.880 --> 00:12:52.670
always provided. He provided the

00:12:52.670 --> 00:12:52.680
twelve

00:12:52.680 --> 00:12:55.190
baskets,

00:12:55.200 --> 00:12:57.530
the fishes, and the loaves. He took care

00:12:57.540 --> 00:12:59.269
of them. He's going to take care of us.

00:12:59.279 --> 00:13:01.970
He's not going to let us go without.

00:13:01.980 --> 00:13:04.129
But you're going to have to be pushing into

00:13:04.139 --> 00:13:05.389
him. You're going to have to have a

00:13:05.399 --> 00:13:07.069
relationship with him. You're going to

00:13:07.079 --> 00:13:10.730
have to have a

00:13:10.730 --> 00:13:10.740
sin-free

00:13:10.740 --> 00:13:12.650
lifestyle as much as possible, living

00:13:12.660 --> 00:13:15.350
holiness. I'm not talking about

00:13:15.350 --> 00:13:15.360
how

00:13:15.360 --> 00:13:17.389
you can't do nothing.

00:13:17.399 --> 00:13:20.389
I'm talking about not living in

00:13:20.399 --> 00:13:23.389
compromise and sin. So you've got to live in

00:13:23.399 --> 00:13:26.509
a relationship where you're on fire

00:13:26.519 --> 00:13:27.710
for God and we're all preaching the

00:13:27.720 --> 00:13:28.850
gospel. And I'm telling you, he's going to

00:13:28.860 --> 00:13:31.129
take care of you. The Lord showed

00:13:31.129 --> 00:13:31.139
me—I

00:13:31.139 --> 00:13:33.110
want to get this documented because

00:13:33.120 --> 00:13:36.050
we're almost there.

00:13:42.060 --> 00:13:43.490
I'll tell one more thing here

00:13:43.500 --> 00:13:45.350
because he keeps reminding me of things.

00:13:48.530 --> 00:13:48.540
In

00:13:50.700 --> 00:13:53.090
2022,

00:13:55.019 --> 00:13:57.829
I had an angelic visitation in a dream.

00:13:57.839 --> 00:14:02.030
And in my dream, the angel told me, 'Great

00:14:02.040 --> 00:14:07.129
judgment is coming in 569 days.'And I

00:14:07.139 --> 00:14:10.310
asked the angel, 'What is the

00:14:10.310 --> 00:14:10.320
judgment?'and

00:14:10.320 --> 00:14:13.430
he said to me, 'I cannot tell

00:14:13.440 --> 00:14:16.069
you. You will have to pray this out. The

00:14:16.079 --> 00:14:18.769
Lord tells me you will have to pray this

00:14:18.779 --> 00:14:21.650
out in the spirit, and he will show

00:14:21.660 --> 00:14:24.170
you and give you revelation of

00:14:24.170 --> 00:14:24.180
this.'So

00:14:24.180 --> 00:14:28.430
I saw on the counter

00:14:28.440 --> 00:14:31.850
510 days. October 2nd is what

00:14:31.860 --> 00:14:33.530
the date came to.

00:14:33.540 --> 00:14:36.170
And so

00:14:36.180 --> 00:14:39.170
it was during Yom Kippur and Rosh

00:14:39.170 --> 00:14:39.180
Hashanah

00:14:39.180 --> 00:14:40.430
of last year.

00:14:40.440 --> 00:14:43.250
And the Lord told me whenever we got

00:14:43.260 --> 00:14:45.410
close to that timeframe, he said, 'I'm

00:14:45.420 --> 00:14:49.009
extending the timeframe and giving more

00:14:49.019 --> 00:14:52.430
time for repentance. I'm going to give more

00:14:52.440 --> 00:14:55.430
time. I'm pushing this back. I'm going

00:14:55.430 --> 00:14:55.440
to

00:14:55.440 --> 00:14:58.910
give the people more

00:14:58.910 --> 00:14:58.920
time.'I

00:14:58.920 --> 00:15:02.389
think I'll end it there. I have

00:15:02.399 --> 00:15:04.790
another video; keep watching. I

00:15:04.800 --> 00:15:06.470
just saw something else—he

00:15:06.470 --> 00:15:06.480
showed

00:15:06.480 --> 00:15:08.629
me in a vision right then, and I

00:15:08.639 --> 00:15:10.490
just saw something. So I'm going to

00:15:10.500 --> 00:15:12.410
tell you in another video what he showed

00:15:12.420 --> 00:15:15.860
me. All right, have a blessed day.

